{"tid":2051996,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"憑iPhone就能讓懸疑片劇透？好萊塢導演：iPhone只能夠好人拿，壞人就要拿 Android","createTime":"2020-06-05T07:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T01:38:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8a179a6ea7b936825b03d73e280ee17b373a7713","tid":2051996,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:45:10.000Z","msg":"雷恩強生（Rian Johnson）在拍攝《鋒迴路轉》時，以 4,000 萬美元的拍攝成本，在全球造就了三億美元的佳績，當他在接受《Vanity Fair》的採訪時，卻不小心爆料，表示蘋果公司其實在電影圈有定下了一個潛規則。<br />\n<br />\niPhone只能夠好人拿，壞人就要拿 Android<br />\n<br />\n雷恩強生表示：「我不知道該不該說，這和色情沒有任何關係，如說出來可能會毀了我下一步神秘電影 &hellip;. 算了！我要爆這個料，這太有趣了！電影內的飾演壞人反派角色，都不能拿 iPhone 出現在鏡頭畫面上。」<br />\n<br />\n其實會說出這個關鍵點，其實是他在構思下一部懸疑作品的過程中感到相當棘手。而當著他無意中透露這訊息後，便自嘲說：「完蛋了，現在每個電影裡有神秘反派角色的電影製作人應該都想了結我。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sci101.news/16457/%e6%86%91-iphone-%e5%b0%b1%e8%83%bd%e8%ae%93%e6%87%b8%e7%96%91%e7%89%87%e5%8a%87%e9%80%8f%ef%bc%9f%e5%a5%bd%e8%90%8a%e5%a1%a2-%e8%98%8b%e6%9e%9c%e6%bd%9b%e8%a6%8f%e5%89%87-%e5%8f%8d%e6%b4%be%e5%ae%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsci101.news%2F16457%2F%25e6%2586%2591-iphone-%25e5%25b0%25b1%25e8%2583%25bd%25e8%25ae%2593%25e6%2587%25b8%25e7%2596%2591%25e7%2589%2587%25e5%258a%2587%25e9%2580%258f%25ef%25bc%259f%25e5%25a5%25bd%25e8%2590%258a%25e5%25a1%25a2-%25e8%2598%258b%25e6%259e%259c%25e6%25bd%259b%25e8%25a6%258f%25e5%2589%2587-%25e5%258f%258d%25e6%25b4%25be%25e5%25ae%2588%2F&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EnjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=2022c499\" target=\"_blank\">https://sci101.news/16457/%e6%86%91-iphone-%e5%b0%b1%e8%83%bd%e8%ae%93%e6%87%b8%e7%96%91%e7%89%87%e5%8a%87%e9%80%8f%ef%bc%9f%e5%a5%bd%e8%90%8a%e5%a1%a2-%e8%98%8b%e6%9e%9c%e6%bd%9b%e8%a6%8f%e5%89%87-%e5%8f%8d%e6%b4%be%e5%ae%88/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f77c30f656935d463dd0875ba7eb919520